<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
{{!--
  ReṼoman landing layout — a minimal, full-bleed shell for the home page only.

  Selected by `:page-layout: home` in modules/ROOT/pages/index.adoc. It mirrors
  the bundle's default.hbs (so the same <head>, navbar, theme CSS, web fonts and
  light/dark toggle all load) but DROPS the docs chrome — the left nav, the
  breadcrumb toolbar and the right-hand TOC — and renders page.contents straight
  into a full-width <main>. The landing markup itself lives in index.adoc (a
  single AsciiDoc passthrough block), so content stays in the docs source tree;
  this layout is just the frame.

  Every other page keeps using the bundle's default.hbs untouched.
--}}
{{> head defaultPageTitle='Untitled'}}
  </head>
  <body class="home{{#with (or page.attributes.role page.role)}} {{{this}}}{{/with}}">
{{> header}}
    <main class="rv-home">
{{{page.contents}}}
    </main>
{{> footer}}
  </body>
</html>
